ium Rush]]'' *''[[The Prince and the Pauper (1990 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1990) *''[[Project X (2012 film)|Project X]]'' *''[[Psycho Cop]]'' *''[[Psycho Cop 2]]'' *''[[Quarantine (2008 film)|Quarantine]]'' *''[[Quarantine 2: Terminal]]'' *''[[Quick Change]]'' *''[[Radioland Murders]]'' *''[[Rambo: First Blood]]'' *''[[Rat Race (film)|Rat Race]]'' *''[[Rebel Without a Cause]]'' *''[[REC (film)|REC]]'' *''[[Red Eye (American film)|Red Eye]]'' *''[[Repo! The Genetic Opera]]'' *''[[The Return of the Living Dead]]'' *''[[The Rocky Horror Picture Show]]'' *''[[Roger Dodger (film)|Roger Dodger]]'' *''[[Rope (film)|Rope]]'' *''[[The Rugrats Movie]]'' *''[[Run (1991 film)|Run]]'' *''[[Run Lola Run]]'' *''[[Running Scared (2006 film)|Running Scared]]'' *''[[The Russians Are Coming, the Russians Are Coming]]'' *''[[Sanctum (film)|Sanctum]]'' *''[[Scooby-Doo! in Where's My Mummy?]]'' *''[[Scrooge (1935 film)|Scrooge]]'' (1935) *''[[Scrooge (1951 film)|Scrooge]]'' (1951) *''[[Scrooge (1970 film)|Scrooge]]'' (1970) *''[[The Set-Up (1949 film)|The Set-Up]]'' *''[[Short Eyes (film)|Short Eyes]]'' *''[[Shrek Forever After]]'' *''[[Shutter (2012 film)|Shutter]]'' *''[[Silent House (film)|Silent House]]'' *''[[The Silent House (2010 film)|The Silent House]]'' *''[[A Single Man]]'' *''[[Sixteen Candles]]'' *''[[The Sitter]]'' *''[[Slacker (film)|Slacker]]'' *''[[Slashers (film)|Slashers]]'' *''[[The Slumber Party Massacre]]'' *''[[Snake Eyes (film)|Snake Eyes]]'' *''[[The Song Remains the Same (film)|The Song Remains the Same]]'' *''[[Sorry, Wrong Number]]'' *''[[Source Code]]'' *''[[A Special Day]]'' *''[[Stan Helsing]]'' *''[[The Strangers (2008 film)|The Strangers]]'' *''[[Stress Is Three]]'' *''[[The Stupids (film)|The Stupids]]'' *''[[Sudden Death (1995 film)|Sudden Death]]'' *''[[Suddenly (1954 film)|Suddenly]]'' *''[[Superbad (film)|Superbad]]'' *''[[The Swimmer (1968 film)|The Swimmer]]'' *''[[Take Me Home Tonight (film)|Take Me Home Tonight]]'' *''[[The Taking of 