[[File:N55 - Spaceframe.jpg|thumb|N55 - Spaceframe]]

'''N55''' is a [[Copenhagen]]-based [[Scandinavia]]n [[art collective]] which was founded in 1994. They work with art and everyday life. Over the years, N55 have achieved international recognition for their projects.{{vague|date=January 2016}}
All of N55's work is freely accessible; their books, manuals  and images can be seen online and are not copyrighted.

N55 advocates the spirit of [[Open-source movement|open-source]] by sharing the information of its products.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://openbikeworks.blogspot.hk/p/what.html|title = OpenBikeWorks: What?|website = openbikeworks.blogspot.hk|access-date = 2016-03-23}}</ref> One of their bike product<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.lowtechmagazine.com/2014/05/modular-cargo-cycles.html|title = LOW-TECH MAGAZINE: Modular Cargo Cycles|website = www.lowtechmagazine.com|access-date = 2016-03-23}}</ref> - [http://www.n55.dk/MANUALS/SPACEFRAMEVEHICLES/DIY.pdf XYZ ONESEATER] is openly shared with the public by disclosing its production manual with construction drawings in pdf downloadable online under their project of [http://www.xyzcargo.com/?page_id=562 XYZCargo].

